            <div class="upload-text">ç‚¹å‡»æˆ–æ‹–æ‹½å›¾ç‰‡åˆ°è¿™é‡Œ</div>
            <div class="upload-hint">æ”¯æŒ JPGã€PNGã€WEBPã€BMP æ ¼å¼ï¼Œå¯åŒæ—¶å¤„ç†å¤šå¼ å›¾ç‰‡</div>
            <input type="file" id="fileInput" multiple accept="image/*">
